title: StarTalk Live! at the Apollo (Part 2)
description: StarTalk’s night at the historic theater in Harlem concludes with some surprises, including a song by Neil Tyson’s nephew, the rapper, Tyson. With Eugene Mirman, Senator Cory Booker, Dr. Ainissa Ramirez, Phoebe Robinson and Maeve Higgins.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
